{"tid":2372891,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[突發] 黎智英案主控 David Perry劈炮唔撈","createTime":"2021-01-20T05:06:18.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T05:10:29.000Z","uid":224120,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"82627d5c88c8a0ca0c968667e002f2b73167b44f","tid":2372891,"uid":224120,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T05:06:18.000Z","msg":"律政司聘用英國御用大律師 David Perry 任主控，負責檢控前年 8 月 18 日壹傳媒創辦人黎智英、民主黨創黨主席李柱銘被控維園非法集結案，惹起英國外相藍韜文等批評。律政司今日發表聲明指， David Perry 關注有關「壓力」，及目前豁免強制檢疫的安排，指出審訊在沒有他的情況下應如期進行，律政司決定委聘另一名律師。<br />\n<br />\n律政司指出，自委聘 David Perry 任主控官之後，有不斷來自英國社會的壓力和批評針對 Perr 參與案件的工作，「當中一些片面的批評將案件與國安法混為一談。」...<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/court/%E4%BB%BB%E9%BB%8E%E6%99%BA%E8%8B%B1%E6%A1%88%E4%B8%BB%E6%8E%A7%E9%81%AD%E8%8B%B1%E5%9C%8B%E6%94%BF%E7%95%8C%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95-%E5%BE%8B%E6%94%BF%E5%8F%B8%E6%8C%87-david-perry-%E9%97%9C%E6%B3%A8-%E5%A3%93%E5%8A%9B-%E6%B1%BA%E5%AE%9A%E6%8F%9B%E4%B8%BB%E6%8E%A7/?fbclid=IwAR24TBeE2iaPqfMz3O8eVs5_j1jIl-Hg-7TYl2QFVff8Wfhkc7oa02W1dAg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595-%25E5%25BE%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%258F%25B8%25E6%258C%2587-david-perry-%25E9%2597%259C%25E6%25B3%25A8-%25E5%25A3%2593%25E5%258A%259B-%25E6%25B1%25BA%25E5%25AE%259A%25E6%258F%259B%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258E%25A7%2F%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR24TBeE2iaPqfMz3O8eVs5_j1jIl-Hg-7TYl2QFVff8Wfhkc7oa02W1dAg&d=CthjHxCXz%2Bl0vOF3eBkmeiNFMfcMnrnh95DLK%2BYL5kQ%3D&h=fb54ecf1\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fcourt%2F%25E4%25BB%25BB%25E9%25BB%258E%25E6%2599%25BA%25E8%258B%25B1%25E6%25A1%2588%25E4%25B8%25BB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E9%2581%25AD%25E8%258B%25B1%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E7%2595%258C%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595-%25E5%25BE%2